OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FNew legislation will require anyone
OL,7,Fwho finds an archaeological object in
OL,8,FJersey to tell Jersey Heritage within
OL,9,Fa fortnight; otherwise, they could
OL,10,Fface imprisonment.
OL,12,FThe Heritage Law, proposed by the
OL,13,FSustainable Economic Development
OL,14,FMinister, Deputy Kirsten Morel, makes
OL,15,Fit compulsory to report and record any
OL,16,Fimportant historical items or
OL,17,Farchaeological sites found in the
OL,18,Fisland.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
