OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FThe proposals were approved
OL,7,Funanimously by the present Jersey
OL,8,FStates Members last week, with 43
OL,9,Fvotes in favour.
OL,11,FIn the proposition, Deputy Morel
OL,12,Fstates that the discovery of the Le
OL,13,FCatillon II hoard in 2012 - the
OL,14,Flargest collection of Iron Age coins
OL,15,Ffound in the British Isles - shows the
OL,16,Fneed for a statutory framework to
OL,17,Fmanage significant finds
OL,18,F"transparently and consistently".
OL,26,@uD@Bsp
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FUnder the new law, any objects that
OL,7,Fpeople find will need to be "properly
OL,8,Frecorded and assessed", and failing to
OL,9,Freport it, hand it over to Jersey
OL,10,FHeritage if asked, or withholding key
OL,11,Finformation could amount to an
OL,12,Funlimited fine and up to 12 months in
OL,13,Fprison.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, anyone who knowingly
OL,16,Fprovides false or misleading
OL,17,Finformation could face up to two
OL,18,Fyears' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FA reward scheme will also be
OL,7,Fintroduced for certain finds, which
OL,8,Fwill be shared between the finder and
OL,9,Fthe landowner.
OL,11,FJonathan Carter, the Chief Executive
OL,12,FOfficer of Jersey Heritage, has called
OL,13,Fit a "transformative law".
OL,15,F"This really brings us into line with
OL,16,Fbest international practice", he adds,
OL,17,Fexplaining that they have been
OL,18,Fpreparing for the law for many years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
