OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FMeanwhile, all significant finds will
OL,7,Fneed to be noted in the publicly
OL,8,Faccessible Historic Environment Record
OL,9,F(HER) - a database held by Jersey
OL,10,FHeritage - to inform future research
OL,11,Fand planning.
OL,13,FImportant historical finds may be kept
OL,14,Ffor museum collections, depending on
OL,15,Fwhether the Viscount qualifies it as a
OL,16,Ftreasure trove or a Jersey national
OL,17,Fantiquity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
