OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FMr Carter adds: "One of the most
OL,7,Fimportant things is it enshrines that
OL,8,Farchaeology is not just about shiny,
OL,9,Fcommercially valuable objects - it's
OL,10,Fabout information.
OL,12,F"We will understand stories about
OL,13,Fwhere we have come from as well as
OL,14,Fwhere we might be going, and it allows
OL,15,Fthat information to be used for
OL,16,Fplanning our future."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
