OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772547083
OL,3,CTreasure hunters could be jailed if
OL,4,Cthey fail to report finds
OL,6,FOther key components of the law
OL,7,Finclude a licensing system for
OL,8,F"intrusive" archaeological
OL,9,Finvestigations in non-designated
OL,10,Fareas, including the seabed.
OL,12,FHowever, licensing will not be needed
OL,13,Ffor activities that remain within the
OL,14,F"depth of the plough soil".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
